{"tid":1205282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"早排睇漫畫,見到會古代戰爭會會俘虜敵軍做陣前卒","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T18:01:46.000Z","uid":48893,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16f3d5d5ad105ea45abd36ec8c06bd1cece244fb","tid":1205282,"uid":48893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:51:33.000Z","msg":"我記得早輪睇一套叫漂流武士 定 王者天下 既漫畫<br />\n有一場係講到話捉打輸左既敵軍做俘虜,係攻城戰既既時間綁住佢地<br />\n要佢地做最前排既陣前卒,用黎消耗對方既遠距離武器 好似箭同 投擲武器<br />\n唔知係邊套到出現過,有冇巴打可以幫我回憶下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b1dcde918c99eb5210e8e05d15e5ec59db714a","tid":1205282,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:01:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2xKpwQd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2xKpwQd.png&h=18a2b7ae&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}